Chlorhexidine.

17
00:01:11.264 --> 00:01:13.171
No iodine.

18
00:01:13.806 --> 00:01:16.669
Oh. Right. Thanks.

19
00:01:17.172 --> 00:01:18.638
[test beeping]

20
