Taking us out.

841
00:45:03.729 --> 00:45:05.295
[groaning]

842
00:45:10.333 --> 00:45:12.566
[♪ Dramatic music playing]

843
00:45:15.279 --> 00:45:16.436
What's the plan?

844
00:45:16.572 --> 00:45:17.910
Draw her close
enough to the star.

845
