she'll get stuck in
the gravity well.

846
00:45:19.517 --> 00:45:21.014
There'll be a time dilation.

847
00:45:21.149 --> 00:45:23.147
-How much of a dilation?
-Is it more than mine?

848
00:45:23.282 --> 00:45:25.216
It'll take her a
month to break free.

849
00:45:26.884 --> 00:45:27.951
Take us in. Ben.

850
00:45:28.087 --> 00:45:29.825
