We need to strap you down.

870
00:46:58.741 --> 00:47:01.477
-Strapping her down.
-Do not strap me down!

871
00:47:02.278 --> 00:47:03.782
Not strapping her down.

872
00:47:03.918 --> 00:47:05.347
-[groans]
-Baby...

