875
00:47:08.585 --> 00:47:09.865
It's not how it's
supposed to be.

876
00:47:09.987 --> 00:47:11.153
I know. I know.

877
00:47:11.289 --> 00:47:12.752
But we're gonna make it work.

878
00:47:14.227 --> 00:47:15.760
You're doing wonderful. my love.

879
00:47:15.896 --> 00:47:18.331
[breathing heavily]

880
