1537
01:22:02.246 --> 01:22:03.546
-[Harvey laughing]
-[sighs]

1538
01:22:03.682 --> 01:22:04.716
Harvey.

1539
01:22:04.851 --> 01:22:06.745
I'm sorry. Sue. I'm...

1540
