-Hi. cutie.

1771
01:42:00.779 --> 01:42:01.875
[kisses]

1772
01:42:02.011 --> 01:42:03.116
Frankie.

1773
01:42:04.810 --> 01:42:06.208
-[grunts]
-You got him?

1774
01:42:06.343 --> 01:42:08.753
