-You didn't pull the slack.

1811
01:43:21.021 --> 01:43:22.378
Just push from above.
Push from above.

1812
01:43:22.461 --> 01:43:24.058
-No. you gotta...
-Pull the slack!

1813
01:43:24.193 --> 01:43:25.495
Okay. I'll get...

1814
