-All right.
-I can't fit my hands in.

1816
01:43:28.433 --> 01:43:29.544
You from the left.
You from above.

1817
01:43:29.627 --> 01:43:31.494
Three. two. one.

1818
01:43:31.629 --> 01:43:32.929
[clicks. bleeps]

1819
01:43:33.065 --> 01:43:36.566
-Oh! Yes! Yes!
-That's a good sound.

1820
01:43:36.701 --> 01:43:37.942
